data.ultrasound_scans: Up to 4 scans - 1 nuchal translucency test covered
data.antenatal_support: Enhanced maternity support via Discovery Health app: create pregnancy profile, track pregnancy milestones, access Women's Health Hub
data.prenatal_care_postnatal_care: We pay for up to R2,400 per day for private ward. Caesarean requires pre-auth
data.delivery_devices: Breast pumps and smart thermometers covered
data.specialists: Up to R6,500 for essential required device fees
data.notes: 12 consultations with gynaecologist during pregnancy. Must register pregnancy on Discovery website 13 weeks before delivery. Access to Parent Sense app for advice and tracking.
